Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.43,0:00:15.30,Staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片源\Nchiwa\N\N\N　壓製\N　xelnaga
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.28,0:01:32.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#11 再見了，日本
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.28,0:01:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完成，有點不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.92,0:01:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確有些觀點比較模糊\N也還有修飾的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，真的寫得很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.09,0:01:49.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.93,0:01:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我有一件事想跟妳商量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.23,0:01:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們接到香港的聯絡\N說是電影完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.44,0:02:01.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，“解放區”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.94,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟業務部門討論過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.28,0:02:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們想趁電影在日本上映時\N發表妳的新書
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.01,0:02:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:12.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四個月後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.16,0:02:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想應該可以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.06,0:02:23.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括以前的作品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想推出一個\N“堇川奈奈奈復活書展”
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.17,0:02:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還請妳多多幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡，我才要請你多多幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來的事情\N和三姊妹也有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.21,0:02:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了參加電影的首映會\N想請老師再去一趟香港
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:43.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去香港嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.85,0:02:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.89,0:02:48.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們當然也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-好棒喔\N-已經一年沒回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.66,0:02:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有，也不是說順便啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.46,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近老師身邊也沒發生什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:03.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說就這樣請你們回去…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.24,0:03:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們被開除了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是，是任務圓滿結束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是這樣，我們就回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.19,0:03:26.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五天後出發到香港\N也就是這個星期五
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會提早一天過去打理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.46,0:03:30.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五天後…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.46,0:03:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家趁最後這段…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.17,0:03:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間過得好快喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.58,0:03:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得打包行李才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.11,0:03:51.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還得跟神保町的大叔們\N說聲再見才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.68,0:03:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書款也要結算清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.89,0:03:57.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.96,0:04:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達也要跟學校的同學道別喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒必要現在就開始感傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.30,0:04:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就平常一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.21,0:04:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們剛才在談
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.69,0:04:31.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期五是結業式對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中午大家去迪士尼樂園玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迪士尼樂園？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳之前不是說很想去嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.60,0:04:40.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然要去，就大家一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.87,0:04:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星期五…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳已經有事了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.97,0:04:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的\N星期五我要回香港
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.75,0:04:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊，那下個月再去好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.32,0:04:59.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼時候回來？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.92,0:05:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說…也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.83,0:05:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要跟姊姊們回香港去了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.13,0:05:13.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.24,0:05:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.30,0:05:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，所以星期五我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:29.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我們來辦個歡送會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.78,0:05:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好耶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辦得熱鬧一點\N菱石也一起參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在日本的最後回憶\N就由我來為妳演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.87,0:05:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見見她喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.17,0:05:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們一定很談得來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.64,0:05:55.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是個愛書狂\N加個“超”都不足以形容
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.54,0:06:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(存起來！)\N老師，這裡面有錢耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把書頁當作保險箱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.42,0:06:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳有她的下落…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是，我一定會通知妳
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.87,0:06:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然說要回香港\N我也覺得很過意不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.31,0:06:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.84,0:06:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，沒辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以至少到星期五為止\N開開心心的過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像過去一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:48.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.50,0:06:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能浪費時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.70,0:06:59.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在看什麼書？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.47,0:07:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“清秀佳人”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有聽過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.14,0:07:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個臉上有雀斑的\N紅髮女孩是主角吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，安總是樂觀進取
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.48,0:07:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至比男生還要堅強\N是個很棒的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.22,0:07:17.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她跟妳有點像
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.62,0:07:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:21.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，這個女孩呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.69,0:07:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她叫黛安娜\N是安的心靈摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,心靈摯友？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.07,0:07:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比誰都重要\N值得尊敬的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本來也希望\N妳能看看這本書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.85,0:07:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，算了\N反正沒有時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.62,0:07:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起\N我今天還得去一個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.93,0:08:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.86,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真高興見到你\N這樣就能和你道別了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.17,0:08:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要去哪裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去香港
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.84,0:08:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.07,0:08:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎樣啦\N你也表現得震驚一點好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.41,0:08:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊\N不要老是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.75,0:08:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了我以外\N也要交別的朋友喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.62,0:08:55.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.22,0:08:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.35,0:08:58.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是我的朋友嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.73,0:09:04.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是把你當朋友啊\N你不喜歡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.40,0:09:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.70,0:09:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.38,0:09:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.22,0:09:27.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要回去香港了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.15,0:09:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.09,0:09:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是有什麼內情\N我都不想聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.06,0:09:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要回去香港\N過平常的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.66,0:09:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是，真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.64,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要保重喔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.24,0:09:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:08.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達，妳去接
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.53,0:10:09.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.00,0:10:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(久美)
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰打來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.68,0:10:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.95,0:10:33.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟同學道別了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.29,0:10:35.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.92,0:10:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要幫我辦一個歡送會
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.46,0:10:40.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.83,0:10:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該…算好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是“支撐的骨之書”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:57.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後只剩一本\N“看穿一切的眼之書”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.78,0:11:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在神保町的大樓\N還是找不到她的蹤跡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.15,0:11:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了，沒關係\N我們連鑰匙都拿到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是這一點\N就是壓倒性的有利
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.29,0:11:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.79,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理想未來的構築\N還差一步就要完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這四年來，辛苦妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起我，請多誇獎朱利亞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱利亞，謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.04,0:11:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,託妳的福，大家都得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.28,0:11:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.65,0:11:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.32,0:11:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的非常優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的世界正需要妳這種人才
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.32,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈姊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:08.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳有沒有“清秀佳人”這本書？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.28,0:13:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搬完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.79,0:13:19.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…艾妮達呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒好…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.60,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-心靈摯友\N-心靈摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.67,0:14:16.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜姊，針線在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(再見了艾妮達)
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.98,0:14:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好，大家都坐好了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.82,0:14:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，艾妮達．金同學的\N歡送會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.86,0:14:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師，小久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.60,0:14:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菱石嗎？\N她說身體不舒服早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.80,0:14:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.80,0:14:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐好啦，艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.87,0:14:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.17,0:14:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去上廁所
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.08,0:14:54.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是大家寫的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.61,0:14:55.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:04.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要做一座大山
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，要做大一點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達，過來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.33,0:15:12.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑一個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一個姿勢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菱石
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體好點沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.52,0:15:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是我說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.18,0:15:32.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.45,0:15:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她看起來很落寞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.82,0:15:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能\N因為艾妮達沒那麼脆弱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她在香港\N一定也會有很多朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.60,0:15:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-拜拜\N-拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.17,0:15:50.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，明天見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.37,0:15:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的不行\N如果參加歡送會的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.95,0:16:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的會想到要跟她告別\N一定會很難過，哭出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達走了之後\N我又會變成孤單一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.56,0:16:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…我無法忍受
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.50,0:16:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會認為\N妳是孤單一個人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.07,0:16:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳怎麼會認為她不會寂寞呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.74,0:16:31.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她當然會很寂寞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.68,0:16:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為要跟妳分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.08,0:16:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是，艾妮達她…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋，笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.35,0:16:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是個笨蛋\N才會這樣逞強
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:43.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是夠了\N你們兩個都是笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.99,0:16:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太相配了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好笨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該更坦率地表達才對
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.38,0:17:05.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.31,0:17:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是已經來不及了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.28,0:17:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交給我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.59,0:17:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興能夠來這所學校唸書
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.52,0:17:18.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會忘記大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.49,0:17:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡，我也是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.27,0:17:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.17,0:17:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.95,0:17:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要跟平常一樣\N明明是不可能辦到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.84,0:18:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.75,0:18:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.13,0:18:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達，我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.33,0:18:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了，不要弄破了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.40,0:18:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳拿著那邊，放出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.37,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.31,0:18:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.64,0:18:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二三
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(艾妮達下次還要再來喔)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:55.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後會有期
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:19:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,see you again\Nhave a nice life，艾妮達
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.33,0:19:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面的時候\N把我的簽名書送給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來妳有這個企圖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.77,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.61,0:19:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然要分開了\N不過，不是永別吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳寫信給我吧\N我也會寫給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:25.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳要打電話給我唷\N我也會打給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.38,0:19:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會把零用錢存起來\N還會去打工賺錢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:32.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春假…可能去不了\N但夏天一定會去香港
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:36.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時候…到時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.36,0:19:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是個大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.64,0:19:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.71,0:19:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾妮達，我最喜歡妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.01,0:19:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小久
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論到了哪裡\N妳都是我的心靈摯友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.29,0:20:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣分手很感人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.13,0:20:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是分手呢\N雖然是分開了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白妳想說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.20,0:20:19.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再過不到一天的時間\N就要離開這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.04,0:20:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了好多事情喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觸很深
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能恢復安靜的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然牢騷一大堆\N不過，真的很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.59,0:20:41.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准看！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.00,0:20:47.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過，如果是偶爾的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.63,0:20:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們來找我玩也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.17,0:20:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.37,0:20:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的榮幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.87,0:20:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈奈姊，臉好紅喔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.01,0:20:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是叫妳不要看嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.41,0:21:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.25,0:21:01.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踩死妳，踩死妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.62,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳再給我笑笑看，殺了妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明明臉都紅了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.65,0:21:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳給我閉嘴，小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.27,0:21:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去住飯店…真的好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係\N住在你們家比較自在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.44,0:21:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且得把你們以前吃掉的份\N一起討回來才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.48,0:21:34.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是厚臉皮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:37.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天的記者會之前\N我們也會陪著妳的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.52,0:21:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書都到哪裡去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.52,0:21:49.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次去追老師的時候\N拿去做瑪姬的飛鳥了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.96,0:21:53.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊\N哎呀，真抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.53,0:21:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們自願的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣比較寬敞舒服多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.64,0:22:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是\N這麼寬又可以收集很多書了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.68,0:22:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.78,0:22:05.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪姬，什麼時候要去書店？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.58,0:22:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂，你們這些書痴\N有沒有在聽我說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.58,0:22:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼，我們去買書吧\N我出錢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.42,0:22:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:18.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳真的不用這麼客氣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.52,0:22:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係，這是禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要再買書了啦\N-光是想像就好興奮喔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.07,0:22:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.36,0:22:54.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師，請跟我一起來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要請妳寫出\N世界上最棒的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:19.24,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珍藏的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.32,0:23:25.12,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是凋零散落
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.19,0:23:28.96,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯有和你的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.03,0:23:34.66,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,深烙在我心深處
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.03,0:23:41.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逐漸轉涼的海邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.17,0:23:46.91,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩人嬉戲的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.98,0:23:51.38,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你曬得黝黑的皮膚
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.45,0:23:56.79,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,融化在西沉的夕陽裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.86,0:24:02.29,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但願牽著的手永不分離
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.36,0:24:09.77,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣長大成人該有多好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.24,0:24:17.27,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在陽光下追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.34,0:24:21.34,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尋找你的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.41,0:24:28.15,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受到戀情結束的預感
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.22,0:24:31.95,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相互依偎

Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.56,0:00:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
